graph LR
    Camera[IMX219 Camera] -->|Frames| Preprocessing[Frame Resize & Norm]
    LiDAR[TFmini LiDAR] -->|Serial Distance| KalmanFilter[Kalman Range Filter]
    IMU[IMU / Gyro] -->|Attitude Data| SensorFusion[Sensor Fusion Node]

    Preprocessing -->|Tensors| YOLO[YOLOv11 Inference]
    YOLO -->|Bounding Boxes| SemanticMapping[Semantic Target Matcher]
    KalmanFilter -->|Filtered Distances| SemanticMapping
    IMU --> SensorFusion

    SemanticMapping -->|Matched Obstacles| ThreatCalculation[Threat Severity Calculator]
    ThreatCalculation -->|Steering Correction Vector| PathPlanner[Local Path Planner]
    PathPlanner -->|Avoidance Commands| FlightController[Autopilot Core]
